Kenyan beauty enthusiasts were treated to the launch of a new product that is a new addition to the iconic Venus range of skin care products.In a country with an estimated population of 15 million youth between the ages of 15 to 29, PZ Cussons is focusing on the growing interest in beauty regimes and skin care products to diversify its offering and grow its share in the East African market. With the introduction of Venus body lotion and Petroleum Jelly with Shea Butter, and Venus Pure Glycerine, the firm said that it had firmly set its eyes on a globally acknowledged growth segment.The launch was held at Safari Park.